batchSwapIn(IVault,BalancerUtils.SingleS.details: Perform a BatchSwap on a given balancerPool.      This function is tailored for formatting and performing swaps given amountsIn on a balancer pool.

params.baseSwap: The base structure for swapping on a balancer pool.
params.deadline: The deadline for the swap to be executed.
params.fundManagement: The structure to indicate who's sending and receiving the funds and where its comming from.
params.limits: The limits for the max/min of each token you're receiving or sending to balancer vault.

batchSwapOut(IVault,BalancerUtils.Single.details: Perform a BatchSwap on a given balancerPool.      This function is tailored for formatting and performing swaps given amountsOut on a balancer pool.

params.baseSwap: The base structure for swapping on a balancer pool.
params.deadline: The deadline for the swap to be executed.
params.fundManagement: The structure to indicate who's sending and receiving the funds and where its comming from.
params.limits: The limits for the max/min of each token you're receiving or sending to balancer vault.

depositAllTokensInForExactBPTOut(bytes32.details: Deposits all tokens in proportion into the Balancer pool in exchange for an exact amount of BPT.      This function is tailored for the deposit type ALL_TOKENS_IN_FOR_EXACT_BPT_OUT.

params.bptAmountOut: The exact amount of BPT to receive.
params.poolId: The identifier of the Balancer pool.

depositExactTokensInForBPTOut(bytes32,IV.details: Deposits an exact amount of tokens into the Balancer pool in exchange for BPT (Balancer Pool Tokens).      This function is for the deposit type EXACT_TOKENS_IN_FOR_BPT_OUT.

params.amountsIn: An array of token amounts to deposit into the pool.
params.minimumBPT: The minimum amount of BPT tokens that the sender is willing to accept.
params.poolId: The identifier of the Balancer pool.

depositTokenInForExactBPTOut(bytes32,IVa.details: Deposits a single token into the Balancer pool in exchange for an exact amount of BPT.      This function is for the deposit type TOKEN_IN_FOR_EXACT_BPT_OUT.

params.bptAmountOut: The exact amount of BPT to receive.
params.enterTokenIndex: The index of the token being deposited in the pool's tokens array.
params.poolId: The identifier of the Balancer pool.
params.tokenAmountIn: The amount of the token to deposit.

initializePool(bytes32,IVault,uint256[],.details: Base function for initializing a Balancer pool.      This function handles the first deposit logic for a newly created balancer pool.

params.fromInternalBalance: To pull from our internal balance in the balancer vault or from our wallet.
params.maxAmountsIn: The amounts to deposit on the initial liquidity deposit.
params.poolId: The identifier of the Balancer pool.
params.tokens: The tokens from the pool to add.

swapIn(IVault,BalancerUtils.SingleSwapBa.details: Perform a SingleSwap on a given balancerPool.      This function is tailored for performing single swaps given a exact amountIN on a balancer pool.

params.baseSwap: The initial parameters needed to formata structured swap on a balancer pool.
params.deadline: The deadline for the swap to be executed.
params.fundManagement: The structure to indicate who's sending and receiving the funds and where its comming from.
params.limit: The limit for the min amount of the token you're accept receiving from balancer vault given a exact amountIn.

swapOut(IVault,BalancerUtils.SingleSwapB.details: Perform a SingleSwap on a given balancerPool.      This function is tailored for performing single swaps given a exact amountOut on a balancer pool.

params.baseSwap: The initial parameters needed to formata structured swap on a balancer pool.
params.deadline: The deadline for the swap to be executed.
params.fundManagement: The structure to indicate who's sending and receiving the funds and where its comming from.
params.limit: The limit for the max amount of the token you're accept sending from balancer vault given a exact amountOut.
